Which AUR helper should I choose?
03.02.2019

Which AUR helper should I choose? If you look at the table https://vk.cc/88yr8q from it, you can see that yaourt and arman are marked as no longer supported. Most users are inclined to yay. To install yay, you can use the script below. Just enter 1 line. The syntax is exactly the same as in pacman.

To install the program write
I-With the package_name

To search for AUR, you don't need to write-Ss
her package_name

To update the entire system including AUR packages
you -Say

The results of the survey

Easy way to install yay
wget git.io/yay-install.sh && sh yay-install.sh


Take the post to your wall so that you can easily find it! Or share it with your friends!

